reviews.review_text: More evolution of McDonalds 10240 King George Blvd, Surrey, BC V3T 2W5.
All i did was redeem a free large coffee through my app and i was greeted with smiles and warmth. Thanks McDonalds!

Fresh, hot food. Well cooked. I like how friendly the staff are when I go in person. Music is a little loud, but other than that, its a great place. I always order my skip the dishes from here as well because I find I get the least amount of errors from this location, if any. Parking: Wheelchair parking spot available. 10-12 parking spots available. Kid-friendliness: They are definitely kid from here. You can get a stroller through the doors. I see people here with babies and older children.
Music is very International, The eating area is pleasant and calm. Enjoy my fast food restaurants Food
The one star is cause they have homeless ppl in there an they smell so bad I couldnt eat my food

I am not by any means a regular here but I do often come to this location late at night around 1030pm as I do shift work. The store manager/supervisor at that time is exceptional. He is very helpful and super friendly and always seems to keep his cool through the craziness of having to deal with some wack jobs around that location I m Pretty sure. I hope McDonald s appreciates your hard work bud your doing a great job!
Came here to grab my mid day gut bomb but was pleasantly surprised! Turns out this location was hit by banksy and I was blessed with some truly breath taking art.
Convenient location with enough parking, friendly staff and quick service. Washrooms could be maintained better.
I suggest everyone to this McDonalds,the food is particularly great
Sadie at the counter was awesome. It was a busy afternoon and though the order was confusing but her execution got McD a 5* rating here. So highlighting Sadie here :)

I came in for fvded and OMG the girl at the till was so amazing her nails were so cute and shiny. I forgot her name but she had a heart pin on her sweater!  she was so funny and nice definitely will be back today amazing customer service even with all the commotion
Waited 16mins for small The Manager apologized and replaced the order with Large fries. Good customer service.

My experience has changed so much since my last review. Your employees has almost become family to me. Maybe you guys made management changes, but this has become one of the better Mcdonalds. Im so happy to come here. Its an amazing team they have.
This is one of the cleanest McDs in Surrey area. Dine-In and Drive Thru Service is both pretty fast. Never had any problems with the food. The lot  has an ample of parking space.

When you want any ice cream just look for Mc Donalds you will find the best one in the town for less than two dollars!!! In this location service was fine and fast. Delicious cone enjoyed just after came out of gym.

Impressed with the speed and the clearly evident manner in which the employees work as a team. It appears to run like a well-oiled machine. Speaking of which, that meme of the ice cream machine breaking probably can head for the hills, because I have never had it stop when I order. Very friendly and well priced.

The pulled the best April fools joke on my friend, he ordered a big Mac no pickles on the app and when he got home the big Mac had  no sauce but still had pickles it was even labeled no sauce and his receipt said no pickles
The manager with the tattoos is so helpful! I lost a receipt and needed it for work and she was more than happy to assist me. Great customer service.

My sister (SB) and I just drove through here (6pm, Tuesday, Feb 23)and the sweetest, most BEAUTIFUL lady was at the second window. I waved at her and she waved back, but I forgot to say hi when she came back to the window. Please say hi for me! She was very sweet, but super professional.
nice place, efficient service, standardized operation, friendly staff
Went into this location for the $2.00 game day deal. Usually when you order in side, places can take along time. Not the case with this location. Not only fast but fresh. Great job!
Thank you for making the 50 burgers so we could hand them out to the homless   wish you guys were allowed to receive tips. Thank you again

Ok, so I have had a very bad day today and after not having anything all day, I went to this place to have a Mac chicken meal. The first time I got my order, I wasn t satisfied with my burger and coffee so I went in and ordered a second one. The girl told me I don t have to pay but I insisted on paying cuz I ate the burger already.  The second one I ordered I told them make sure there s no Mac chicken sauce but I got sauce in it again.  I tried to go back to drive thru to complain my coffee spilled all over my car.  So I went inside and talked to the manager, who was not very sympathetic so I just walked away and started cleaning my car outside.  I saw $10 on the ground, I picked it up, asked the guys if it s theirs but they said no. By the ways my meal costed me about the exact same amount.  Within a few mins, a really sweet girl, exactly like an  angel  came out with the money in her hand for my meal and a towel to help me clean my car. Omg I mean how this girl changed my whole day!! I can t describe it ... she was insisting on cleaning my rug and told me tat there s a new order coming up for me. She was so nice and sweet that I felt bad about the whole situation. She comforted me hugged me, and so I was curious wat is she?? asked her name, she said her name is Miriam, and she is from Iraq. I stopped myself after she left and started thinking about; if everybody was like her, there would not be any racism, any fights, nor any trouble in this world. I m sure the manager sent her to make sure I leave happy but she went way beyond anyone s expectations. I m in the same field myself for more then 15 years but I don t think I have done or seen anything like this before. I really want to thank all the members of this McDonald s, specially Miriam for making my day !!!
Its a nice place. The price is excellent, but the quality of the fries is minimal
Super friendly staff!

one time i came here and ordered a poutine on the touch screen thing an it just froze. Literally didnt get past the screen; so I just waited five minutes till an order of poutine came up, I took it, an got out real fast. was never caught and still dont know if it was mine

As usual the food is consistent. The staff were polite and attending even though it was quite busy. My favoutite: a bacon  cheeseburger with three chicken nuggets, fries a pack of mayo and a pack of ketchup also put inside.

Mmm. Satisfied my sugar/salt cravings. I tried the plain old value burger meal and it was enough to eliminate the immediate hunger pangs plus it didnt push my daily calories over the top. Its not the smartest choice if you are watching your nutritional intake but how much can it hurt once in awhile.

Taking the time to fill out a review for this location. Despite being in possibly one of the roughest neighborhoods in all of the Lower Mainland: it stands as bright exception with energetic staff, good food and a tidy environment. Drive thru or Dine In, try it out yourself.
This location is very busy and is in the bad area of town. The staff are friendly the store is relatively clean and the food is good.
Quick service and fresh chicken nuggets!
Thank you Bradley for great customer service, i was there last week for some hot pancakes meal with my sister and daughter. Bradley was very helpful and positive. i will come back again.
Excellent place for McDonalds food
Fast food fast service made fresh to order
I would rather drink mds coffee over Tims any day , an my 1 pound puppy loves the smiles the or guys give her everyday she gets excited cause she loves there coffee too lol
It is a fun place for the kids or adults the food was fast and good

Great place for adventure and famiky fun Down hill mtn. Biking hiking, beautiful views during climp on lift up to 7200 ft on lift to New suspension bridge. Golfing ans great meals of all varieties of food. You cant misss this place as a world class resort and a 500 million expansion in plan, Go and have a great day
Fast customer service. Food was good. Surprised its not in the mall but its still convenient to visit
Great staff team work, make orders faster and clean. Very delicious burgers and many drinks available. Drive-thru.
One of my favorite mcds having grown up in Surrey. We had breakfast and all our food was hot and fresh. No complaints!
Always a nice experience
Products as always are great. Quick and nice service with the curb mobile order.
Have always had good service and food. Drive thru is fast. Never had a meal messed up.
Food was fast and they got the order correct.
Good food. But theres Always homeless people waiting at the end of drive through. Theres also too many weird people that eat inside
I only have the sausage Mc muffin breakfast with extra sausage no drink or anything x2...love it...
Excellent service!!! I rarely eat at McDogballz BUT i was gasing up and all i could smell was THE FRIES

This is the first time Ive used it and Ive got to say I like it it was very fast and she was so polite when she came to my window way to go guys
Good dining just a little chilly with air conditioning on
A little busy but the food was fast, and all items were right. Staff were friendly.
I am satisfied with their service. I got my order at the curbside really quick.

My kid likes Fries and Chicken nuggets and off course Ice Cream, we like burgers

Hot food, quick service. Overall a good breakfast!

This place is amazing to eat.The food provided here is awesome than other mc donalds

Great place to have breakfast or a light snack

Ordered via the app, food came out hot and with a great smile.

Nice place and ambient Staff is quick And kids would love it

food was amazing and staff were awesome. great place to hang out
